# Claim Boundary

Petri Dish Pro is an educational and research simulation sandbox.

It can simulate coarse organism interactions, produce density maps and population curves, export reproducible run artifacts, and support model-thinking.

It cannot claim clinical validity, diagnostic validity, treatment authority, wet-lab proof, biosafety clearance, regulatory evidence, or real organism prediction without external validation.

Every run must preserve: `educational_research_simulation_only`.
